snippet.title: HGTV's Biggest Scandals Ever
snippet.description:
Chip and Joanna. Drew and Jonathan. David and Hilary. If you're a big fan of Discovery's home improvement and real estate network HGTV, you know these names very well, and you've likely spent dozens of hours watching these telegenic hosts help homeowners craft their dream homes. But despite appearances to the contrary, some HGTV hosts and the teams behind the shows they front have (allegedly) been at the center of some pretty serious scandals. From a property dispute at the Magnolia Market to a police helicopter outside Tarek and Christina El Moussa's house, here are some of HGTV's biggest scandals ever.
